<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM3.2">
<l>ituveṉ pukuntatiṅ kantō vippoykaik kevvāṟu vantāy</l>
<l>matuviṉ ṟuḻāymuṭi mālē māyaṉē yeṅka ḷamutē</l>
<l>vitiyiṉmai yālatu māṭṭōm vittakap piḷḷāy viraiyēl</l>
<l>kutikoṇ ṭaraviṉa ṭittāy kuruntiṭaik kūṟai paṇiyāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Oh! What has happened here? How did You come to this pond?</l>
<l>O Māl [wearing] a crown with honey[-filled] tulsi! O dark One! Our Nectar!</l>
<l>We will not [acquiesce] for that due to lack of good fortune.</l>
<l>O skilful Lad! Do not rush!</l>
<l>You leaped and danced upon the snake!</l>
<l> Do give [back] the clothes that are on the wild lime tree!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
